  "title": "CNC MACHINIST",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for dependable, innovative candidates who can work confidently and independently.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate CNC machines to perform all tasks</li>\n  <li>Perform first article inspection on all parts according to mechanical drawing.</li>\n  <li>Understand specifications of the task at hand and the desired result</li>\n  <li>Prepare and load raw materials and parts onto the machines</li>\n  <li>Prepare a test run to check if the machines produce outputs according to specifications</li>\n  <li>Set machines to complete full cycles to fabricate large number of parts</li>\n  <li>Supervise the machines while they execute the tasks and make any necessary adjustments to produce a better result</li>\n  <li>Able to coordinate with design department and QC department for development of new designs.</li>\n  <li>Inspect and measure finished products and compare them with requirements to determine if the process has been completed properly</li>\n  <li>Check and maintain and upkeep machinery daily</li>\n  <li>Learning and applying the latest relevant knowledge to the work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Analyzing information and finding the best solutions to problems</li>\n  <li>Skill in operating CNC machinery and tooling as well as precision measurement tools</li>\n  <li>Ability to read and interpret mechanical documents and drawings</li>\n  <li>Good communication abilities</li>\n  <li>Plan and optimize materials, tooling and fixtures.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ayyakannu Buvaneswaran , Ministry of Recruiters Pte Ltd , EA: 12C5314, EA Personnel : R1217664</strong></p>",
